{
  "id": "RAW_e6332f7a",
  "title": "“写代码 15 年了，为什么我还是没腻？”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247825548&idx=3&sn=08d76e5a9b793e263974eb69698f90b2",
  "date": "2025-12-02 11:53:00",
  "author": "CSDN",
  "siteName": "CSDN",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-category=\"正文\" data-mpa-template-id=\"1440\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">\n    <div>\n     <div style=\"padding:10px;text-decoration:inherit;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(240, 242, 246);font-family:inherit;border-style:solid;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;line-height:25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">【CSDN 编者按】在很多开发者的职业叙事中，15 年往往意味着倦怠、麻木、被无穷无尽的需求和工单压得喘不过气。但本文作者给出了另一种视角：在软件开发这个高速变化、永远有坑、永远有惊喜的行业里，依然有人能从一行小脚本、一个冷门的系统洞察、一次微不足道的自动化里找到持续 15 年的热爱。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;line-height:25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://iwriteaboutcode.blogspot.com/2025/11/what-still-fascinates-me-about-software.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://iwriteaboutcode.blogspot.com/2025/11/what-still-fascinates-me-about-software.html</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">翻译</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">&nbsp;| 郑丽媛</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:1px;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">出品 | CSDN（I</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">D：CSDNnews）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天我突然意识到，相比很多同事，我其实过得</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">还算</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不错</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而他们过得又比很多现实生活中的朋友更不错。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但真正让我意外的是：15 年了，我居然还能从软件开发里获得快乐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">人生里能保持 15 年吸引力的事并不多。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我能想到的另一个，就是开车 —— 一条空旷的公路、一辆靠谱的车，甚至都不需要音乐，轮胎与柏油路的摩擦声就足以让我心安。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在我看来，编程跟开车很像：纯粹、有沉浸</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">感、有属于自己的小世界。所以今天我想聊聊：15 年后，编程、代码、软件开发，究竟还有什么值得让我着迷。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100093015\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d45a915&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FPn4Sm0RsAuhl4ayeuEiaB8J2KJaGvr0DMfWInznkxoE2YlrAeqh8ctwYgSG7rd1bkPhLicH4V3sLTqHn99bC5Vbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252192\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2c5b48b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QuwjkSP1G6wEJHaJCLTONqlcQexqRgJcIICxofIOJs6B6tWBfibb7now%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"392\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">那些微小到几乎没人注意，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">却让我“爽到飞起”的改进</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"394\" data-end=\"432\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">别误会，我当然也喜欢那些带来巨大业务价值的大功</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能 —— 那是我拿工资的理由。但真正让我“兴奋”的，是那种</span><strong data-start=\"448\" data-end=\"481\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">每天能省五分钟、每周能省一小时、只有我自己知道价值的小优化</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"549\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">例如，上周我写了一行代码，把某个老是重复出现的错误引导到另一条执行路径。这个 Bug 手动修只需要十分钟，但现在？我再也不用处理了。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"614\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一行代码背后，是我十五年的经验积累、对系统细节的理解、对数据流的洞察——就为了那种“啊我懂了，我能搞定”的瞬间。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"616\" data-end=\"634\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">这种体验，比写一个大功能还让</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">人满足</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252191\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0d6be04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QDyP5HTUOXsPlJWd79yygiasaqXicpN7ibIfqiak5WFpaxE1mGxxpfmMjiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"677\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">写下一行代码背后，站着几十年、几千人的努力</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"763\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">下次你在 VS Code 里敲一个字母，自动</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">补全啪一下弹出时，停下来想一秒：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了这一行补全，多少人贡献了代码？多少人免费修过 Bug？多少想法从七十年代传递至今？</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"786\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们今天的每一次敲击，都踩着前辈们的肩膀：有些人已经去世，有些人再也没写过代码，有些人曾为你每天用的某个 API 做过演讲……这一切共同组成一个让人惊叹的事实：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">软件世界是少有的 “知识共享无边界”的行业。</span>所有程序员都能在 StackOverflow 上互相帮忙修算法 Bug，只因为那是个有意思的问题。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1010\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而绝大多数现实世界的行业不会这样</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;——你很难看到哪位木匠愿意把“祖传手艺”免费告诉陌生人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252190\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c02173a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0QtgZAx8xsoTReptvArfwbn9MvHGVfV98Qkl5PMRS6MCt2ljwLJwoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1046\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">布尔值背后的灰色地带：技术讨论永远比代码本身复杂</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1048\" data-end=\"1066\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">理论上，技术世界是最“布尔”的世界：</span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1070\" data-end=\"1079\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要么跑，要么挂</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1082\" data-end=\"1095\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要么编译通过，要么报错</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1098\" data-end=\"1110\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要么 1==1，要么不等</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1156\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但实际呢？<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">任何一个看似简单的决定，都能变成激烈讨论、政治博弈、甚至心理战。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1158\" data-end=\"1219\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有趣的是，这些讨论往往不是坏事。其他开发者、其他团队、甚至你的老板都有可能提出有价值的观点，帮助你更完整地理解问题。而这些“灰色地带”让软件开发充满人味——代码世界是布尔的，但团队</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">世界永远不是。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1324\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">庆幸的是，我现在的位置仍让我能“亲自下</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">场写代码”。讨论完之后，最终落地的那一行代码 —— 才是我真正期待的事情。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252189\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=064d4bfc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q3SAo8dibFicWvibnB5u4gdHLgb2AbA6UJ8VImKnyW92hibqZefwpDbPYAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">中间件开发的乐趣：让两个巨大系统听懂彼此</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1364\" data-end=\"1398\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我近年的大部分工作是写中间件，说实话：</span><strong data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1398\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这是我最喜欢的活之一。</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1400\" data-end=\"1414\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中间件看似只是“转发数据”：理解系统 A 的输出，理解系统 B 的输入，处理常规情况，兜住边界情况，设计稳定的转换逻辑。但里面可以玩的东西非常多，例如数据校验、数据转换、监控、异常追踪、防火墙与代理、编码问题、部署、可观测性、稳定性设计等等。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1569\" data-end=\"1593\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">哪怕连最无聊的中间件，都能让我脑子一直保持兴奋。毕竟，我一个人就可以把完整的中间件从头到尾写完，并且三年后它仍能稳定运行。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1642\" data-end=\"1683\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不是因为我多厉害，而是因为输入/输出</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">够稳定，数据量足够大让逻辑变得“超级可靠”。这种感觉，像养了一缸自动运</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">行的生态鱼缸 —— 自己偶尔看一眼监控，都觉得很舒服。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252188\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1f2214d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0jqAkXB2hEohZkOqYzXVsmJtnNRQncYh54ZQOpcC5ZGSicYFgtBZP4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1731\" data-end=\"1765\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">技术圈里对热点的吵闹，让我越来越享受“做一个安静的旁观者”</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1767\" data-end=\"1780\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">关于 AI，我只想说两点：</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1785\" data-end=\"1808\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（1）还记得几年前大家把“低代码”吹上天的声音吗？</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1812\" data-end=\"1851\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（2）奇怪的是，程序员自动化别人工作时从不担心，但轮到自己被自动化时不少人都开始慌了。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1853\" data-end=\"1879\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">老实讲，我每天都能找到 ChatGPT 的使用场景：小自动化脚本、大流程优化、文档生成、调试辅助、快速查资料（代替我自己摸索几十分钟），那些喊着“LLM 完全没用”的人，对我来说比 AI 狂热吹捧者还奇怪。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2038\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他们吵得越厉害，我就越喜欢在旁边</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">安安静静地用 AI 工具赚钱、写代码、提效。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252187\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44efccae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QGHX4EaTS3AknUHvnayNiaLnANlsxF3g1JR5q9HIdppdNd8c8uyuC05w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"2045\" data-end=\"2077\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">所谓“枯燥的业务系统开发”，其实是最能激发创</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">造力的地方</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"2079\" data-end=\"2120\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我的职业生涯几乎都在“老系统 + 工业级软件架构”里打滚。有人觉得这很无聊，总是改小 Bug、加小功能、在巨大单体里扩一个子模块或者受制于几十年前的架构决策——</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">但你知道吗？入行 15 年，我</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就是喜欢这种约</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">束。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">因为正是这些限制，让软件开发对我来说充满了乐趣。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很多有缺陷的系统既僵化又难以改变，但恰恰在这种情况下，总有空间去做定制</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开发、寻找务实的解决方案，或者自己写代码在两个大型系统之间搭建桥梁。还有那些 “居家版 DevOps” 解决方案，可能不如成熟工具那么花哨，但能以 20% 的工作量达到 80% 的效果。</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2354\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;2286&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;2354&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">更重要的是：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这种定制开发的</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;2286&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;2354&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">需求永远都很明确。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">需求、输入输出都有明确的定义，而且需求是即时存在的。我从来不需要考虑产品市场匹配（PMF），因为市场本身就迫切需要我的产品，而且通常会明确告诉我他们需要什么 —— 而不是我到处问 “有人需要这个吗？”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对我来说，在时间、预算和架构的限制下工作，正是我现在坚持下去的动力。我已经写了太多的 for 循环和 if 语句，普通的软件开发对我来说已经有些重复了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当然，你也不能整天只设计系统，否则会脱离实际，看不到那些从宏观视角会忽略的小问题。所以我的工作中需要有实际的编码部分 —— 而且我更希望这些编码工作能有趣、有挑战性，而不是每天重复写</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\">那些早就写过几千遍的代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252186\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1a3932b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q3hdXZlicTdZH0gDHXnpe9sZjuIdKFqdo93tKQ8icc5U5JcMkFHiadezlA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2452\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">软件开发，是我生活里最不无聊的部分</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2502\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">每当我对工作有点厌倦，我只需要去一趟超市，看一看普通人的“NPC 模式”。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你会瞬间意识到：</span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2504\" data-end=\"2521\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong data-start=\"2504\" data-end=\"2521\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能坐着写代码，是一种奢侈。</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2523\" data-end=\"2535\" style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就算是最糟糕的日子，我们也能接触到一个充满不变真理的世界：信息可以自由获取，身边的人通常都很聪明且通情达理。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">但每次我踏入现实世界，都会明显感觉到巨大的落差</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">&nbsp;—— 我总觉得，在我遇到的人里，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;2609&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;2648&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">大概有一半的人随时处于“主系统维护中”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">再加上软件开发这个领域如此多样化，没有任何人能彻底理解其中的十分之一。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">所以在入行十年后，这个职业带给我们的回报，早已不只是金钱 —— 还有很多身边人无法获得的、意想不到的收获。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">因此，我有信心，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">15 年后我会再写一篇文章：《入行 30 年，我依然为软件开发着迷的那些事》。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "一位拥有 15 年编程经验的开发者分享了他在软件开发中持续保持热情的原因，包括微小优化、知识共享、复杂讨论和中间件开发的乐趣。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "一位拥有 15 年编程经验的开发者分享了他在软件开发中持续保持热情的原因，包括微小优化、知识共享、复杂讨论和中间件开发的乐趣。",
  "summary": "文章作者以其 15 年的软件开发经验，探讨了在行业中保持热情的深层原因。他指出，真正的满足感往往来自于那些不为人知、却能显著提升效率的微小优化。同时，作者强调了软件开发领域独特的知识共享文化，以及技术讨论中人际互动的复杂性与价值。他还分享了中间件开发的乐趣，即在系统间构建稳定桥梁的成就感。面对技术热点（如 AI），作者主张保持冷静，利用 AI 工具提升效率。尤其值得一提的是，作者认为在看似“枯燥”的业务系统开发中，受限于旧系统、预算和架构的约束，反而能激发独特的创造力，找到务实且高效的解决方案。文章最终总结编程是一种奢侈且充满乐趣的职业。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "微小而高效的优化是开发者持续获得满足感的重要来源",
      "explanation": "通过对系统细节的深入理解，实现日常工作流程中看似微不足道的自动化和 bug 修复，能带来巨大的个人成就感和效率提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "软件开发领域独特的知识共享文化是行业进步的基石",
      "explanation": "程序员社区乐于互相帮助、分享经验，这种无边界的知识共享机制，是其他行业难以比拟的，也是技术持续演进的动力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在约束条件下解决复杂问题更能激发创造力",
      "explanation": "在老旧系统、预算和架构限制下，寻找定制化、务实的解决方案，反而能带来独特的挑战和乐趣，并明确需求，实现高价值交付。"
    }
  ],
